    "created_at": "2026-02-21T04:11:37Z",
    "updated_at": "2026-02-21T04:11:37Z",
    "body": "If you use fish shell, you can use this to dynamically switch palettes depending on the system's light/dark mode:\n\n```fish\nstatus is-interactive; or exit\n\nfunction apply_theme --on-variable fish_terminal_color_theme\n    switch $fish_terminal_color_theme\n        case light\n            starship config palette catppuccin_latte\n        case dark\n            starship config palette catppuccin_mocha\n    end\nend\n```",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
